{
  "stem": "18770.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My family finds probably the one kosher restaurant in Tokyo-- a kosher restaurant in Tokyo in 1940.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, it boggles the mind, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I think they find it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember Japan being extremely clean.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And people-- the family marvel at that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I remember them talking about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The street-- I mean, not another speck of paper, nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You know, people wearing masks if they have a cold, so they won't spread germs-- very different, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And already some kind of early-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] how can I put it?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sort of, like, hints of America because Japan is influenced by America the way Poland was not before the war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that, for instance, it's the first time I see those barbershops with the rotating poles which no longer exist.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that's what [LAUGHS] they used to have.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and in fact, I go to get a haircut.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they let you sit, like, on a hobbyhorse while they cut your hair-- sort of American ideas, but still very, very Japanese.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now there's talk-- more talk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Are we going to be able to get into America, this promised land that I'm hearing stories about?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or is it going to-- are we going to end up having to go to South America?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so how-- when you left Japan, you-- obviously, by this time, whatever mechanism they had for getting papers, you had papers?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We have papers to take us as far as Canada.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not America yet-- it's still not clear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We go to America-- I think, when we're on the boat going from Japan to Canada-- that we hear the election results that Roosevelt has been re-elected.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
